about.aboutContent:
Â 

Welcome to the Toronto Sustainable Transport Application,
developed by Graduate Students at the University of New Brunswick, Department of Geodesy and Geomatics Engineering.

This app aims to show:Â 
Where you go; How you get there; When you go; and how these options affect your CO2 emissions.

Use the routing app to get directions, then change your vehicle, time of day/year to determine how the emissions output will be affected.


Spatial Data sets:Â City of Toronto, Esri
